July 19th, 2022 X-Wing Vassal news

Module website is at: http://xwvassal.info
Tutorial guide for this module: http://xwvassal.info/guide

New v9.4.0 X-Wing module is out. Match it with the latest Vassal client software v3.6.7 from http://vassalengine.org. A compatibility break which occured when Vassal client v3.6.6 has been fully resolved. Get the latest and greatest for both the X-Wing module and the Vassal client!

Windows players: ctrl(held) + LeftClick on ships (while they are on the map) to access the ship mouse interface (new feature in 2019)
Mac players: rightmost option(held)-click on ships
